            <description><![CDATA[【专家：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%86%8B%E5%B0%BF%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8A%A5%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%B0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%86%8B%E5%B0%BF%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8A%A5%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%B0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#憋尿属于不是不报时候未到#</span></a> 后果很严重！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%86%8B%E5%B0%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E6%86%8B%E5%B0%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#尽量少憋尿#</span></a> 很多人都有过憋尿的经历，早上赖床不想起床憋，工作太忙没空上厕所憋，憋得不行了才去上厕所，终于浑身舒坦了。专家提示，总是憋尿，膀胱功能变弱，会导致想尿的时候尿不出来，不想尿的时候却误以为要尿。长期憋尿还有9种危害👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4904960576389135" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly1he9k20zv3lj60o00didgq02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/VxMMEESAlx085GRNt6t201041200f5ML0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=864x486.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685294326&amp;ssig=VvgyEkI7iG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/FBw6NbnBlx085GRNF2ms010412009vc30E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1685294326&amp;ssig=AbUdwQljsp&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/Z9vTvJoylx085GRNtuF2010412005RO80E010.mp4?label